						               													<description>You are a half-blood between vampire and werewolf. You have power! You can be a vampire! A werewolf! A human! You are one of the most powerful creatures in history &amp;mdash; but you were too powerful. All humans, vampires and werewolves are now searching for you to kill. You lost your home, parents, friends, everything by them. There is nothing left except bloody revenge.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Night of Horror Dice is a simple dice game. You have three health points for each turn. First, choose your ability. You can use one ability from human, vampire and werewolf. Each abilities has unique effects. Then, pick up three enemy dices from pouch and throw. As the result you gain or lose your health, catch them or they might runaway. You can throw another three dices or stop your revenge. All your captured enemies are your score. Strong enemy gives more score. If you caught four or more enemies in a type, you got additional score. Careful about your health, and catch enemies as many as possible.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
